<lyrics>[V1]
 Chis čs ma! Chi anukfillit
 Chi tikba yaŐĪ e l čshke;
 Okchalinchi chia hak oŐĪ
 Ai okchaŐĪya pi b čnna:
 P čsk' okchaŐĪya
 Ish pimashke, Chis čs ma!

[V2]
 Chim aiimpa holitopa
 Afoluplit chiya hosh,
 Chibai imp čt e maŐĪya k čt,
 NaŐĪ pi yukpa fehn čshke:
 Chishno pulla
 Yakoke, il ahnishke.

[V3]
 &quot;Il čpp čt sa haknip mak osh
 H čchiŐĪ boshulli hoke;
 P čsk' okchaŐĪya sia hokaŐĪ,
 S čthahaŐĪn čt, oh  čp√°,&quot;
 Ish achi na,
 E chim antihiŐĪy čshke.

[V4]
 Isht ishko yaŐĪ ish ishi m čt,
 &quot;Il čpp čt s čssish oke,
 LaŐĪwa iŐĪ hlatapa hoka,
 Moma k čt h čsh ishkashke,&quot;
 Ish achi na,
 Yakoht il aiash čshke.

[V5]
 Pishno ak inli hok čno
 Immi h čpia keyu;
 Nan ai člli chinto fehna
 Isht pi  člhtoba hatok;
 Chis čs immi
 Pi hohchiefo hoke.</lyrics>
